21:11.479 --> 21:13.355
Ferris Bueller's on line two.

21:24.617 --> 21:26.117
Hey, Mr. Rooney, how you doing?

21:26.202 --> 21:29.746
Listen, I'm sorry to disturb you at work,
but I'm not feeling very well today

21:29.830 --> 21:32.958
