that I might need.

21:36.045 --> 21:37.545
Have a nice day.

21:52.228 --> 21:53.478
Mr. Peterson?

21:55.189 --> 21:57.816
I think I owe you an apology, sir.

21:57.900 --> 22:00.652
- Well, I should say you do.
- I...

22:01.112 --> 22:02.404
I, I, I...

22:02.488 --> 22:05.323
Well, I think you should be sorry,
for Christ's sake.

22:05.408 --> 22:07.158
A family member dies

22:07.243 --> 22:10.704
and you insult me. What the hell
is the matter with you anyway?

22:11.580 --> 22:13.039
Well...

22:13.124 --> 22:14.582
I really don't know, sir.

22:14.667 --> 22:16.501
I mean, I didn't think
I was talking to you.

22:16.585 --> 22:18.003
I thought I was talking
to somebody else.

22:18.087 --> 22:21.464
You know, sir, that I would never
deliberately insult you like that. I...

22:21.549 --> 22:24.968
I can't begin to tell you
how embarrassed I am.

22:25.428 --> 22:27.470
- What?
- Pardon my French,

22:27.555 --> 22:28.888
but you're an asshole.

22:28.973 --> 22:31.099
- What do you want?
- Asshole.

22:31.183 --> 22:34.477
Absolutely right, sir.
You've hit the nail right on the head.

22:34.562 --> 22:36.104
Find out where she is.

22:36.188 --> 22:38.773
