Do you read me?

22:38.941 --> 22:41.026
Loud and clear, Mr. Peterson.

22:41.110 --> 22:43.236
Call me "sir," goddamn it!

22:43.320 --> 22:46.281
- Yes, sir, yes, sir.
- That's better.

22:47.867 --> 22:50.326
And you just mind
your p's and q's, buster.

22:50.411 --> 22:52.662
And remember who you're dealing with.

22:53.497 --> 22:55.540
Bueller, Ferris Bueller.

22:57.501 --> 23:00.462
Now, I'm a little scared 'cause
what if he recognizes my voice?

23:00.546 --> 23:03.548
- Impossible. You're doing great.
- Yeah?

23:06.635 --> 23:09.054
She's in... Wait.

23:10.973 --> 23:12.140
Rooney!

23:14.477 --> 23:16.227
Rooney, calm down!

23:16.312 --> 23:17.645
Just a moment.

23:18.606 --> 23:20.315
Ed! Get in here!

23:22.026 --> 23:24.402
Just a little office difficulty, sir.

23:24.487 --> 23:26.071
Rooney, I don't have all day
to bark at you.

23:26.155 --> 23:28.656
So I'm gonna make this
short and sweet.

23:28.741 --> 23:30.283
It's great. Perfect. I love it.

23:30.367 --> 23:34.829
I want my daughter out in front of the
school in 10 minutes by herself.

23:34.997 --> 23:36.706
I don't want anybody... What?

23:36.791 --> 23:38.666
