He'll think something's up.

23:38.751 --> 23:39.751
- Cover it.
- You.

23:39.835 --> 23:40.960
- Talk.
- You.

23:41.045 --> 23:42.337
- Talk.
- Come on.

23:43.297 --> 23:44.714
