23:45.132 --> 23:47.217
Rooney! Rooney.

23:47.301 --> 23:48.551
Yes, yes.

23:48.636 --> 23:51.346
Listen here, pay attention.
I changed my mind.

23:52.014 --> 23:53.848
I want you out
in front of the school with her.

23:53.933 --> 23:56.392
