by God.

23:58.354 --> 24:00.730
On second thought,
we don't have time to talk right now.

24:00.815 --> 24:03.358
We'll get together soon
and we'll have lunch.

24:04.235 --> 24:05.693
What the hell is wrong with you?

24:07.279 --> 24:08.655
Wait.

24:08.739 --> 24:10.115
- Where's your brain?
- Why'd you kick me?

24:10.199 --> 24:11.741
