into oblivion, and then,

24:53.826 --> 24:56.077
and then,
you deliberately hurt my feelings.

24:56.162 --> 24:59.372
No, I did not deliberately...
I didn't deliberately hurt your feelings.

24:59.498 --> 25:01.958
- Really?
- Really, no. No, I didn't.

25:05.045 --> 25:06.254
What are you doing?

25:06.338 --> 25:08.006
See you later, pal, I'm going home.

25:08.090 --> 25:11.050
- No, no, come on, don't do that.
- Have a nice life.

25:11.427 --> 25:14.262
Cameron, wait a minute.
Cameron, come back.

25:14.346 --> 25:18.349
I didn't mean to lose my temper.
I'm sorry. It was uncalled for.

25:19.768 --> 25:21.853
- You serious?
- Yeah.

25:29.653 --> 25:30.987
Here you go.

25:33.324 --> 25:34.574
