28:23.452 --> 28:24.744
How about that?

28:28.457 --> 28:30.124
Come on, live a little.

28:34.296 --> 28:37.924
Once again, let me tell you how deeply
saddened I am by your loss. I...

28:38.175 --> 28:40.134
I had a grandmother, once.

28:42.054 --> 28:43.554
Two, actually.

28:43.639 --> 28:47.100
Deficits. Who will have to pay that
eventually? Anyone? Anyone know?

28:47.476 --> 28:50.520
"Man that is born of woman
