29:13.460 --> 29:14.836
I'll take grief.

29:16.964 --> 29:17.964
Great.

29:27.224 --> 29:28.683
Oh, Sloane, dear.

29:29.143 --> 29:31.018
Hurry along now.

29:33.313 --> 29:35.148
I guess that's my dad.

29:35.482 --> 29:37.150
- Yeah.
- Gotta go.

29:40.446 --> 29:41.863
Mr. Rooney...

29:43.031 --> 29:47.827
- Ed, you're a beautiful man.
- Thank you.

29:49.538 --> 29:52.540
I wanna thank you
for your warmth and compassion.

29:54.168 --> 29:57.128
Higher "what" rates? Anyone?

29:57.212 --> 30:01.924
