Any questions so far?

30:02.134 --> 30:03.217
Shit.

30:05.888 --> 30:08.389
- Hi.
- Do you have a kiss for Daddy?

30:08.515 --> 30:09.932
Are you kidding?

30:20.861 --> 30:23.571
So, that's how it is in their family.

30:28.410 --> 30:32.538
- Hi, Cameron. You comfortable?
- Hi, Sloane. No.

30:35.918 --> 30:37.460
What are we gonna do?

30:37.753 --> 30:40.087
The question isn't:
What are we going to do?

30:40.172 --> 30:42.048
The question is:
What aren't we going to do?

30:42.132 --> 30:43.883
Don't say we're not going
to take the car home.

30:43.967 --> 30:46.177
Please don't say we're not going
to take the car home.

30:46.261 --> 30:48.262
If you had access to a car like this,

30:48.347 --> 30:50.473
would you take it back right away?

30:51.475 --> 30:53.017
Neither would I.

31:24.424 --> 31:26.467
Hey, Ferris, don't go so fast!

31:26.552 --> 31:29.303
- Red line, red line, red line.
- Ferris, get out!

32:28.530 --> 32:29.572
Thank you.

32:29.656 --> 32:30.698
Save Ferris.

32:30.782 --> 32:32.116
God loves you, you're very generous.

32:32.200 --> 32:33.868
Save Ferris, save Ferris.

32:33.952 --> 32:36.787
Save Ferris Bueller. Save Ferris.

32:37.205 --> 32:38.873
