so if you could help out...

32:45.297 --> 32:48.090
- Go piss up a flagpole.
- I'm sorry?

32:48.592 --> 32:50.134
- You should be.
- Hey...

32:50.218 --> 32:51.844
Hey! Hey...

32:51.928 --> 32:53.220
